FBIS3-25351 "drafr032_d_94003" FBIS-AFR-94-032 Document Type:Daily Report 16 Feb 1994 SOUTHERN AFRICA Mozambique Dhlakama Reaffirms Abandonment of Military Option MB1502151794 Maputo Radio Mozambique Network in Portuguese 1030 GMT 15 Feb 94 MB1502151794 Maputo Radio Mozambique Network Language: Portuguese Article Type:BFN [Excerpt] Afonso Dhlakama, leader of the Mozambique National Resistance [Renamo], has assured (Arnold Guntz), head of the African Affairs Department in the FRG's Foreign Ministry, that his organization has abandoned the military option once and for all. The Portuguese news agency, LUSA, reports that Dhlakama and (Guntz) met in Maputo yesterday. [passage omitted]
